Project Goal

Build a production-quality AI-powered Cyber Safety Platform with a modern UI, scalable backend, privacy-first architecture, and modular design. The platform should feel like a commercial cybersecurity SaaS product rather than a student project.

Core Requirements
Professional landing page
Authentication (optional if time permits)
Responsive dashboard
Modern UI with dark/light mode
React frontend
FastAPI-ready backend integration
Modular architecture
Professional animations
Accessible design
AI Analysis

Create modules for:

Email Scanner
URL Scanner
File Scanner
Message Scanner
Prompt Injection Detection
Social Engineering Detection
QR Code Scanner (future-ready)
Malware Risk Analyzer

Each module should:

Accept user input
Show scan progress
Display confidence score
Explain reasoning
Generate a human-friendly recommendation
Multi-LLM Engine

Design the backend so every request can be sent to multiple LLMs.

The system should:

Collect responses
Compare outputs
Aggregate findings
Produce one explainable final verdict
Context Box

Before every scan include:

"Tell us anything that may help analyze this item."

Examples:

Where did you receive it?
Was it expected?
Who sent it?
Any additional context?
Human-like AI Opinion

Every scan should conclude with:

Summary
Risk explanation
Recommended actions
Confidence level

Written naturally, like a cybersecurity advisor.

